dct_title_s: Jerusalem die heilige viereckete Stadt in Grundt gelegt und eigentlich abgemalet
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, settlements, places of historical interest.
"37" -- top left margin ; "38" -- top right margin.
Appears in Bünting's Itinerarium sacrae scripturae, Helmstadt: Jacobus Lucius, 1582. Second edition.
